{"tid":1661552,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民陣指警方反對周日九龍遊行因為主題包括重組警隊","createTime":"2019-10-18T07:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T10:19:17.000Z","uid":35790,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd99dc3e0f597ce1ad1d77df3362ff5bab19a32","tid":1661552,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:19:50.000Z","msg":"民陣指警方反對周日九龍遊行因為主題包括重組警隊<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-18 HKT<br />\n<br />\n民陣星期日舉行的九龍遊行，警方發出反對通知書，民陣將會提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n副召集人陳皓桓形容，警方的決定「離譜」，質疑警方無考慮過去與民陣開會期間的討論，當時警方交通部認同民陣的路線對他人影響是最少。<br />\n<br />\n陳皓桓說，今次主題是「獨立調查、重組警隊、五大訴求、缺一不可」，批評警方因為是持份者之一而發出反對通知書，形容是「斬腳趾避沙蟲」。<br />\n<br />\n他提到，大部分市民在民調中反映要重組警隊的訴求，市民要透過遊行集會表達訴求，但若不批准舉行和平遊行，反問市民如何表達意見。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486936-20191018.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486936-20191018.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=b8ccb9bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1486936-20191018.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=afdd57ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1486936-20191018.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3ddefe7c6f66b2f8053304c194abfdf970d07124","tid":1661552,"uid":35790,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:21:28.000Z","msg":"陳皓桓說，今次主題是「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獨立調查、重組警隊、五大訴求、缺一不可</span></span>」，批評警方因為是持份者之一而發出反對通知書，形容是「斬腳趾避沙蟲」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"941af5e191776cd16e1ba6ae528022d9eff709ef","tid":1661552,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"171dfcb6bc5e9df1a451b576fe6dc422d964e35f","tid":1661552,"uid":14897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T07:24:28.00